But America has gone much worse and not only
that, but the films they are producing are

00:39:50.550 --> 00:40:00.690
very dangerous films and really damaging the
whole world.

00:40:00.690 --> 00:40:07.339
They don't know what sin they are committing,
for thousands and thousands of people in the

00:40:07.339 --> 00:40:19.670
world have taken to all kinds of very destructive
ugly ideas.

00:40:19.670 --> 00:40:28.460
Freud, all right, he's ousted - finished,
he's done already a great harm.

00:40:28.460 --> 00:40:40.839
But what about these films, they are now very
much impressing our Indian directors.

00:40:40.839 --> 00:40:46.430
I think all these directors are guiding Indians
to hell.

00:40:46.430 --> 00:40:51.829
The whole thing is so absurd and so dirty.

00:40:51.829 --> 00:40:56.030
For an Indian mind it is really inconceivable.

00:40:56.030 --> 00:41:08.559
Even, I have seen Americans can't bear it,
it has gone that bad.

